3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a method to improve the generalization capabilities of a model, which is a key aspect of AI.
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with classification tasks, which can be related to natural language processing.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with image classification, which falls under the domain of multimedia.
